casebody.data:
No. 419,

Misc.

Miranda v. Arizona. John P. Frank for petitioner. Darrell F. Smith, Attorney General of Arizona, and William E. Eubank and Gary K. Nelson, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

Sup. Ct. Ariz. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. The case is transferred to the appellate docket.
